description:
Dang, rockin' me with the Sweet Disposition on the overhead was choice for a late, warm afternoon lunch in SF.

The once-in-a-while IPA hops went straight to the head while I was waiting for my $20 Lobster Fries. Wasn't a fan of the peppers'n'onions I usualky omit from my food but I let it go d/t the nice buzz and cooly ice water.

I can see myself in a 1 on 1 here but Only w/ DACs that can manage to keep their phone off the table and down a beer a two over the indie-alt soundtrack. They have nice orange lights.



//I wrote this funny-headed thanks to a Racer 5. Catch me at a Juice Shop next for a PPC an Immunity Shot measure up ;}
